>LCD Soundsystem的2025年美国巡演日期是：</strong></h2><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>7  - 凤凰城，亚利桑那州 -  M3F节</strong><br /><strong>8  - 加利福尼亚州圣地亚哥 -  Petco Park的Gallagher Square ^</strong></p><p><strong>四月</strong><br /><strong>22  - 德克萨斯州奥斯汀 -  emo</strong><br /> <strong>23  - 德克萨斯州奥斯汀 -  emo的</strong><br /><strong>24  - 德克萨斯州奥斯汀 -  emo</strong><br /> <strong>26  - 德克萨斯州达拉斯 -  Deep Ellum的工厂 *</strong><br /> <strong>27  - 德克萨斯州达拉斯 -  Deep Ellum的工厂 *</strong><br /> <strong>30  - 洛杉矶新奥尔良 - 卫生剧院 *</strong></p><p><strong>可能</strong><br /><strong>1  - 洛杉矶新奥尔良 - 卫生剧院 *</strong><br /> <strong>3  - 佐治亚州亚特兰大 - 可口可乐Roxy *</strong><br /> <strong>4  - 佐治亚州亚特兰大 - 可口可乐Roxy *</strong></p><p><strong>六月</strong><br /><strong>7  - 西班牙巴塞罗那 -  Parc delfòrum（Primavera Sound Barcelona）</strong><br /> <strong>8  - 法国巴黎 -  Bois de Vincennes（我们爱绿色）</strong></p><p>在标志性的纽约乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-winter-2024-nyc-winter-function-residency-buy-tickets-3795250">在纽约举行的年度“冬季功能”节目中，这一新的日期是在标志性的纽约乐队完成的。</a>演出是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-share-pulsing-new-single-x-ray-eyes-on-streaming-3808595">在11月发行“ X射线眼”之后的</a>。 “ X射线眼”标志着该小组的第一本新材料 - 除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-release-their-first-song-in-five-years-new-body-rhumba-3320310">独立的“ New Body Rhumba”，Noah Baumbach的2022年电影<i>White Noise</i></a> （自2017年复出专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lcd-soundsystem-american-dream-review-2133039-2133039">American Dream</a> ”以来在2010年的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/lcd-soundsystem-this-is-happening-what-do-you-think-778717">这发生</a>”之后。</p><p>这首歌是LCD Soundsystem <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-will-release-a-new-album-in-2025-3806010">即将发行的专辑的主打单曲，据报道将于明年发行</a>。除了发行“ X射线眼”之外，墨菲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-murphy-shares-update-on-whats-shaping-up-to-be-a-new-lcd-soundsystem-album-3808727">还分享了即将到来的唱片的最新消息</a>，说：“不要问我什么时候，因为我们仍在努力。但是，发行新音乐真是太好了。”</p><p>去年，LCD Soundsystem <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">接管了日落插槽期间格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）的金字塔阶段</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">该集合的五星级<i>NME</i>评论说</a>：“包装好的金字塔场彼此紧紧抓住，并伸向天空，因为LCD的10首歌曲大师班自然而然地以“所有我的朋友”结束<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">。</a>这首歌和这一刻是格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）最好的表现，在制作中的记忆和美好时光，仍然要来：&#39;<i>如果太阳升起了，我仍然不想错开，那就是对我们的好处使我们站起来</i>。”这就是开始的方式。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-2025-us-tour-3831914">LCD邮政Soundsystem宣布2025年美国巡回演唱</a>会首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
谁赢得了“叛徒”第三季？ https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-kill-3827323?utm_source=rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = the-campaign = the-the = the-campaign = the-the-the-the-the-traitors-traitors-season-3-who-who-was-was-killAdam Starkey Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:30:40 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3827323 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）与“叛徒”的第三场选手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>剧透前方</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">谁赢得了“叛徒”第三季的职位？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）与“叛徒”的第三场选手" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经过两个赛季和世界各地的其他几个版本，<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>叛徒</em></a>仍然是电视上最受关注的真人秀之一。</p><p>由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）主持，第三季看到25名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡中争夺价值高达12万英镑的奖金。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/best-tv-shows-2025-stranger-things-bear-andor-wednesday-3826471">20个大型电视节目在2025年期待</a></strong></li></ul><p>在城堡中，选出几名参赛者是“叛徒”，他们必须掩盖自己的身份并消除“忠实者”以要求获得奖项。但是，如果忠实的人设法通过每日圆桌会议驱逐所有叛徒，那么所有幸存的参赛者都将赢得现金奖。</p><p>英国广播公司（BBC）去年将演出续签了第四季，还播放了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-uk-celebrity-edition-announced-3786092">九集名人版</a>。</p><h2>谁在第一周离开了<em>叛徒</em>第3季？</h2><p>开幕剧集介绍了所有25名参赛者，尽管他们甚至在踏入城堡之前就进行了火车车辆的转折。三名参赛者不得不提名自己离开火车，不知道结果会是什么。</p><p>选择离开火车的参赛者是亚历山大·龙蒂（Alexander Dragonetti），福齐·法西尔（Fozia Fasil）和杰克·马林纳·布朗（Jack Marriner-Brown），他们都暂时从比赛中撤离。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：尹吕（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg" alt="叛乱者在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> YinLü在“叛徒”中：BBC和Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒受到了传播博士的怀疑和智力的威胁，尹吕是第三季中第一位被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>放逐：内森·希德（Nathan Khider）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text">内森（Nathan）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达感到怀疑，但八名球员投票赞成驱逐39年历史的房地产顾问内森（Nathan）。该决定基于他安静的举止之外的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="基思在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text">基思在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思（Keith）被认为是一个坚强而讨人喜欢的角色，成为叛徒谋杀的第二个人。</p><p><strong>放逐：Elen Wyn（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="叛徒的埃伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">埃伦（Elen</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他球员挂钩后，加上她相信大多数叛徒将是“坚强的女性”之后，翻译者埃伦（Elen）被淘汰了。</p><p>她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>：“一旦您的名字出现在那里，就很难拯救自己。”</p><p><strong>放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="叛徒阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827329" class="wp-caption-text">阿玛尼（Armani）是第三季中第一个离开的叛徒：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>球员们在第三集中设法消除了他们的第一个叛徒，因为阿玛尼的勇气和指挥态度迅速与她作战。她自己的姐姐迈亚·古维亚（Maia Gouveia）承认对自己的行为有怀疑，她的命运被封锁了。</p><h2>谁在第二周离开？</h2><p>在情节的第二周开始时，以前淘汰了选手亚历山大·龙妮蒂，福齐亚·法西尔和杰克·马里纳·布朗，被带回了一个挑战，使他们挂在森林中的笼子里。</p><p>玩家只能节省三名悬而未决的参赛者中的两名，然后从这一点开始就加入了比赛。在提出令人信服的争论之后，亚历山大和弗齐亚被球员救出，而出生于约克郡的市场商人<strong>杰克被送回家</strong>。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Maia Gouveia（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg" alt="迈亚在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827331" class="wp-caption-text"> Maia在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在她的姐姐在最后一个圆桌会议上被驱逐出境之后，叛徒选择谋杀玛雅，以取出可能是强大的对手。她的去世还对弗雷迪（Freddie）引起了怀疑，弗雷迪（Freddie）以前在上一场圆桌会议上以她为目标。</p><p><strong>放逐：卡西姆·艾哈迈德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="叛徒的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text"> Kasim被驱逐出每个人的沮丧：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>这是不幸的必然性，卡西姆被从小组中被驱逐出来，因为他只是太好了，而且 - 至少在杰克的脑海中 - 因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼（Armani）是在莫名其妙地为他保证他之后，在上一个圆桌会议上封锁了命运的人，其他球员说服他也是叛徒。</p><p><strong>放逐：泰勒·史密斯（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827710" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827710" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827710" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg" alt="泰勒叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827710" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管弗雷迪（Freddie）发热量，但当莱昂（Leon）和莱恩（Leanne）开始怀疑他们内心圈子中的某人时，潮汐在圆桌会议上与29岁的理发师泰勒（Tyler）脱颖而出。他的离开引起了利维（Livi）的特别激动的反应，利维（Livi）因决定而流泪。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Livi Deane（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg" alt="利维叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828057" class="wp-caption-text"> Livi在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>为了将弗雷迪（Freddie）进一步加入射击线，叛徒决定杀死26岁的美容师和模特丽维（Livi）在圆桌会议上的情感爆发之后。</p><p><strong>放逐：丹·伯德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg" alt="丹在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828064" class="wp-caption-text">丹在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在剧集之前没有在任何人的雷达上，但丹在挑战期间的谎言还是在圆桌会议上撤消了他。 Leanne和Minah都面临着他的面对面，他们将焦点放在了他的隐藏真理上。</p><h2>谁在第三周离开？</h2><p>第三周的第一次谋杀案有一个转折。叛徒挑选了四名参赛者玩一场名为“死亡比赛”的纸牌游戏，其失败者将被谋杀。</p><p> Leon，Alexander，Fosia和Anna被选为比赛。每轮的获胜者都免于谋杀。</p><p>其余的球员在下一个任务中发现了比赛的结果，他们在棺材里找到了幸存的球员。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Fozia Fasil（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="Fozia Fasil" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829330" class="wp-caption-text"> “叛徒”中的Fozia：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在对阵莱昂的指甲决赛中，弗齐亚是死亡比赛结束时最后一位站在死亡比赛结束的球员。然后，她被叛徒谋杀了。</p><p><strong>放逐：琳达·兰德斯（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829332" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829332" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829332" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg" alt="琳达" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829332" class="wp-caption-text">琳达在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>经过几天的怀疑，包括在圆桌会议上进行了几次密切的电话，琳达成为了第二次从游戏中驱逐的叛徒。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829726" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829726" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829726" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg" alt="安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829726" class="wp-caption-text">安娜在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在夏洛特被招募为叛徒之后，她和米纳（Minah）决定安娜在城堡的时间结束，她“不再需要”。在比赛中，安娜曾被怀疑是一名叛徒，在被选为死亡比赛之后，觉得叛徒出去了。叛徒以前曾试图招募她，但她拒绝了。</p><p><strong>放逐：Alex Oleksy（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="叛徒的亚历克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829736" class="wp-caption-text">亚历克斯在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在整个比赛中，亚历克斯大部分都在雷达下飞行，但是厨房里的评论不佳证明了他的垮台。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：丽莎·库普兰（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831243" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831243" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831243" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒的丽莎·库普兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831243" class="wp-caption-text">丽莎在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>叛徒认为她是一个无法撒谎的值得信赖的信徒，在经过一些尖锐的观察之后决定谋杀英国国教牧师丽莎。</p><p><strong>放逐：莱昂·杰克曼（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg" alt="莱昂叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831242" class="wp-caption-text">莱昂在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>忠实者在死亡比赛后的举止发生了变化后，对零售商店经理莱昂（Leon）感到怀疑，导致他最亲密的盟友反对他。</p><h2>谁在第四周离开？</h2><p>该节目的最后一周以相对直截了当的方式开始，残酷地谋杀和扭曲的国际象棋比赛。</p><p>仅剩两个圆桌会议，剩下的八名选手之间的紧张局势达到了历史最高的高度。然而，游戏将通过嘲笑的秘密力量将其脑海中的脑海。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：乔·斯科特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831230" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg" alt="乔·斯科特（Joe Scott）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831230" class="wp-caption-text">乔在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>乔（Joe）是该小组的非常声音的成员，经常在圆桌会议上提出想法 - 无论他们是错误的。但是，这最终与他无能为力，因为叛徒认为谋杀他将传达强烈的信息。</p><p><strong>放逐：米纳·香农（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831236" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831236" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831236" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="米亚" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831236" class="wp-caption-text">米亚在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>米纳（Minah）从一开始就以叛徒的身份发挥了一场强大的比赛，并避免了很长时间的怀疑，但最终，这一切都变得脱节了。最后，叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）将她扔到公共汽车下，进行了最后一票，这意味着她被驱逐出城堡。</p><p>被淘汰后，最后一位剩下的叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）选择招募弗雷迪（Freddie），他勉强接受了邀请。</p><p><strong>放逐：弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg" alt="弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831608" class="wp-caption-text">弗雷迪在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管夏洛特欺骗了新招募的叛徒弗雷迪谋杀Leanne，但在节目的倒数第二集中没有谋杀，尽管她没有盾牌，但她无法被谋杀。通过弗雷迪（Freddie）笨拙的撒谎尝试，他被忠实的洞察力，随后被驱逐出境。</p><p>在任务中获得最多的钱后，弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）获得了先知的力量，使她能够在一次私人会议上发现一名选手的真正身份。在一个戏剧性的悬崖峭壁中，我们发现她选择揭露夏洛特。</p><p><strong>放逐：夏洛特·伯曼（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831925" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831925" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831925" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors.jpg" alt="夏洛特叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Charlotte-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831925" class="wp-caption-text">夏洛特（Charlotte）在“叛徒”（BBC/Studio Lambert）中</figcaption></figure><p>弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）发现夏洛特（Charlotte）是叛徒之后，这成为两者之间的激烈战斗，以使其他人说服前一天晚上的事件。尽管夏洛特（Charlotte）的鳄鱼眼泪，但正是弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）设法推翻了最后的叛徒 - 尽管当她离开时，没有一个信徒被告知夏洛特的真实身份。</p><p><strong>放逐：亚历山大·龙蒂（Alexander Dragonetti）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831929" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831929" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831929" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors.jpg" alt="亚历山大在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Alexander-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831929" class="wp-caption-text">亚历山大在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在最后的圆桌会议上绊倒后，亚历山大成为了火炉周围的明显目标。尽管他是一个忠实的人，但他在整个系列赛中都被怀疑，并且这些怀疑在最后一轮中变得太突出了。</p><p><strong>放逐：弗朗西斯卡·罗恩·普洛登（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831928" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831928" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831928" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main.jpg" alt="弗朗西斯卡叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Francesca-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831928" class="wp-caption-text">弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>夏洛特（Charlotte）对弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）的信誉的袭击事实证明，在壁炉比赛中造成了巨大破坏，因为她成为莱恩（Leanne）的关键投票后，在最后一轮比赛中被驱逐出境。</p><h2>谁赢得了<em>叛徒</em>的决赛？</h2><p><strong>获奖者：杰克·布朗（Jake Brown）和Leanne Quigley（信徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners.jpg" alt="杰克和莱恩叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-winners-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831930" class="wp-caption-text">杰克（Jake）和莱恩（Leanne）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>今年的系列赛由28岁的项目经理杰克（Jake）和28岁的莱恩（Leanne）赢得，他是指甲技术员的前士兵。在壁炉中取消了亚历山大和弗朗西斯卡之后，两人将94,600英镑的最终奖项分配。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">谁赢得了“叛徒”第三季的职位？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛丽莲·曼森（Marilyn Manson）在性侵犯调查后不面临任何指控https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-to-face-no-charges-after-sexual-assault-investigation-3831911?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=marilyn-manson-to-face-无负责人 - 性行为攻击Emma WilkesFri, 24 Jan 2025 21:27:01 +0000 Music NewsNews..Metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3831911 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>洛杉矶县地方检察官内森·霍克曼（Nathan Hochman）说，这是不足的证据，而指控却超出了时效的法规</p><p>玛丽莲·曼森（Marilyn Manson）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-to-face-no-charges-after-sexual-assault-investigation-3831911">性侵犯调查后，没有面临任何指控</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/marilyn-manson-medios-y-media-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>检察官证实，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marilyn-manson">玛丽莲·曼森（Marilyn Manson）</a>对性侵犯和家庭虐待指控进行了长达多年的调查后，不会面临任何指控。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-unmasked-director-karen-mcgann-interview-watch-channel-sex-abuse-allegations-culture-change-3828738">“玛丽莲·曼森：揭露”导演卡伦·麦甘（Karen McGann</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://apnews.com/article/marilyn-manson-no-charges-sexual-assault-investigation-46dba2ffb7e02249a13621a79f3e5c40" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">美联社报道</a>，</em>洛杉矶县地方检察官内森·霍克曼（Nathan Hochman）解释说，这些指控超出了局限性，并且没有足够的证据对曼森。</p><p>霍奇曼说：“我们已经确定，家庭暴力的指控属于限制法规，我们不能在合理的怀疑中证明性侵犯指控。”</p><p>他补充说：“我们认识到并为挺身而出的妇女的勇气和韧性表示赞赏，他们挺身而出，分享报告并分享她们的经验，我们感谢她们与调查的合作和耐心。”</p><p> 2021年，《震惊摇滚艺术家》的前任伙伴，演员埃文·雷切尔·伍德（Evan Rachel Wood）被指控曼森（Manson） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">是布莱恩·华纳（Brian Warner） - 修饰，虐待和操纵</a>。在2022年，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-alleges-marilyn-manson-essentially-raped-her-on-music-video-shoot-3144594">声称华纳在拍摄了他2007年歌曲的“心形眼镜（当心脏指导手”时）时“基本上强奸</a>”了她的“相机上”。</p><p>伍德最初发表声明后，其他许多妇女对音乐家提出了指控。其中包括<em>《权力的游戏》</em>演员埃斯梅·比安科（Esme Bianco），他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-esme-bianco-files-lawsuit-against-marilyn-manson-2931423">提起了指控性侵犯，身体虐待和人口贩运的诉讼</a>。</p><p>华纳强烈否认了这些指控，他将其描述为“现实的可怕扭曲”。这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sues-evan-rachel-wood-for-defamation-3173472">反击了木材，以造成诽谤</a>和情绪困扰。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-drops-defamation-lawsuit-against-evan-rachel-wood-3816324">去年11月放弃了诉讼</a>，并同意向她支付327,000美元的律师费。华纳和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/games-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-and-marilyn-manson-reach-settlement-in-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3386310">比安科于2023年1月达成了庭外和解</a>。</p><p>去年，比安科（Bianco） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-star-esme-bianco-hits-out-at-la-prosecutor-over-mishandled-marilyn-manson-rape-allegations-3801830">在洛杉矶县地方检察官乔治·加斯科（GeorgeGascón）袭击了她所说的“不幸”的强奸指控</a>。</p><p>她说，等待检察官对指控做出决定的最后四年是“绝对的痛苦”，并补充说她必须“追捕”地方检察官办公室以进行最新消息。 2024年10月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sexual-abuse-case-new-leads-evidence-3801970">加斯康透露，办公室的性犯罪部门对他们对音乐家的调查正在审查中</a>。</p><p>曼森尚未就针对他的指控发表评论。但是，比安科说，她“深感失望”，但对调查结果并不感到惊讶。</p><p> “在我们有毒的受害者文化中；缺乏对强制控制的理解，亲密伙伴关系中性侵犯的复杂性质以及不支持治愈现实的局限性法规；比安科在Instagram上写道：“起诉通常面临着无法克服的障碍。” “再次，我们的司法系统使幸存者失败了。”</p><p>她补充说，责备不是在案件中的检察官或侦探均失败，而是“使他们这样做的系统绑在集体事实后面。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFN8y4py4aU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns: